  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effects of an anti-inflammatory drug (Lotemax®)
      on the surface of the eye and tear film (a film that coats the eye which is made up of oil
      and water).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
